  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to study the effects of growth hormone (GH) replacement
      on the heart. The investigators will study these effects in people who have been cured of
      acromegaly and then have developed growth hormone deficiency (GHD, not enough growth
      hormone).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
